Convert 'balance' into a categorical feature by grouping with start and end of interval as:¶

(0, 500, 1000,1500,2000, 2500, 5000, 7500, 10000, 15000, 20000, 25000)¶

def visClassifierResults(model_w_parameters):
    viz = ClassificationReport(model_w_parameters)
    viz.fit(X_train, Y_train)
    viz.score(X_test, Y_test)
    viz.show()

    roc = ROCAUC(model_w_parameters)
    roc.fit(X_train, Y_train)
    roc.score(X_test, Y_test)
    roc.show()
